Business Brief -- Varco International Inc.:
   Letter of Intent Is Signed
   To Buy Drilling Gear Firm
The transaction consists of $37 million in cash and an
estimated payment of $2 million based upon Shaffer's 1992
operating results, Varco said.
   The acquisition is subject to execution of a definitive
agreement, board approval, financing and appropriate
government review, Varco said. It is expected to close in
March.